WEBVTT

00:07.527 --> 00:08.825
Shane Smith:
<i>This week on</i> Vice:

00:08.861 --> 00:11.928
<i>The final battle against ISIS
in Mosul.</i>

00:19.238 --> 00:21.772
Aris Roussinos: We're now
in the suburbs of Mosul,

00:21.807 --> 00:24.440
<i>which is, today,
a huge battlefield.</i>

00:24.476 --> 00:28.545
Smith: <i>And then, a lost
generation of Iraqi youth.</i>

00:28.580 --> 00:30.180
Isobel Yeung: Oh, my God.
What's that?

00:31.916 --> 00:34.584
Yeung: You don't mind your son
having these photos on his phone?

